      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">Dunky operates a hosted AI agent platform. When you subscribe, we provision a dedicated container running your personal AI agent. You configure the agent through a web dashboard, connect it to messaging platforms and data services, and interact with it via chat, Slack, or email.</p>
